<plot>A touching and informative tribute to British comedy actor Richard Beckinsale, who died aged just 31 in 1979. Archive clips of his TV and film career (including 'Porridge' and 'Rising Damp') are featured alongside interviews with friends, co-stars and his actress daughters, Samantha and Kate.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?598112</url></doc>
